Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing’ game
MADISON, Wis. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Wisconsin Lottery’s “All or Nothing” game were:
01-02-06-07-08-09-10-11-14-16-20
(one, two, six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven, fourteen, sixteen, twenty)
